          <h2>1. About VeVolt</h2>
          <p>
            VeVolt helps electric-vehicle drivers view charging locations, range,
            routes and savings. It can use optional location, search Open Charge
            Map, open directions, scan QR codes, search businesses by postal code,
            maintain local records, receive community contributions and organize
            shared private chargers through VeVolt Condo.
          </p>
          <p>
            VeVolt does not control hardware, reserve public charging stations or
            receive charging payments.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Permitted use</h2>
          <p>Use VeVolt only for lawful, personal purposes. You must not:</p>
