          </ul>

          <h2>3. Third-party information and estimates</h2>
          <p>
            Open Charge Map and other provider data may be incomplete or outdated.
            Distance, range, cost and savings are estimates; energy, price and other
            local values may be entered by users.
          </p>
          <p>
            Confirm important information with official sources or the charging
            location operator before making travel, charging, payment or safety
            decisions.
          </p>

          <h2>4. User data and privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Personal vehicle details, saved locations and charging history remain
            on the device. VeVolt has no email/password account and does not sync
            those personal records. The backend receives the minimum data required
            to validate Premium, process postal searches, operate the Community and
            provide VeVolt Condo, as described in the
            <a href="/en/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>5. VeVolt Community content</h2>
          <p>
            By publishing a confirmation, price, rating, comment or photo, users
