            Contributions use an anonymous community identifier. The app lets users
            report content, block its contributor on the device and delete their own
            report. VeVolt may hide or remove reported or abusive publications.
            Community reports are not operator confirmations.
          </p>

          <h2>6. Premium, Google Play and VeVolt Condo</h2>
          <p>
            Subscriptions are managed and charged exclusively by Google Play.
            Premium provides detailed history, CSV export, advanced metrics, the
            expanded Market catalog and Condo administration. Invited residents can
            participate without Premium.
          </p>
          <p>
            Condo reservations only organize private chargers entered by users.
            They do not confirm physical availability, control equipment, reserve
            public stations or process energy payments.
